name: The Olympia Dining Table
description: The Olympia is a rectangular dining table, desk or reception table boasting clean, elegant lines standing on two distinguishing shaped pedestals with a straight outer edge and softer curved inner edge for a contemporary look. The table is also available in any of Davidson's luxury signature timbers and lacquers to suit a range of decors, offering a versatile approach when choosing furniture. The Olympia has pedestals with a luxurious, antiqued, brushed brass trim, which has been beautifully inlaid to run flush through the centre of each leg. A larger size option at 3.6 meters upwards is available with two cruciform pedestals to provide extra support for a larger table top.
